Hurry. Go.

290
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:40,020
You...

291
00:18:40,020 --> 00:18:40,620
Are you alright?

292
00:18:40,980 --> 00:18:42,980
Why were you going inside?

293
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:45,460
What were you doing?

294
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:47,500
What if you didn't get out?

295
00:18:47,580 --> 00:18:48,380
My father's photo

296
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:49,780
could have been burnt.

297
00:18:53,620 --> 00:18:54,220
Ma'am.

298
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:55,020
Mom!

299
00:18:55,420 --> 00:18:56,060
Mrs. Feng.

300
00:18:56,540 --> 00:18:57,460
- Chunsheng.
- Hongling.

301
00:18:57,460 --> 00:18:58,620
Go to get a tricycle for me.

302
00:18:58,620 --> 00:19:00,460
My mother has a heart problem.
She's in danger.

303
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:01,220
I'll borrow it from Dong.

304
00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:02,380
I'll be back soon.

305
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:04,340
How are you, Mrs. Feng?

306
00:19:04,340 --> 00:19:04,940
Mom.

307
00:19:16,180 --> 00:19:16,860
Hongling.

308
00:19:17,540 --> 00:19:18,460
- Guohua.
- How is she?

309
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:19,540
My mother is dying.

310
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:20,220
Get in the car.

311
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:20,740
OK.

312
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:21,700
Please give me a hand.

313
00:19:21,980 --> 00:19:22,460
OK.

314
00:19:23,220 --> 00:19:23,820
Thanks.

315
00:19:23,820 --> 00:19:25,020
Excuse me. Excuse me.

316
00:19:25,020 --> 00:19:26,060
Excuse me. Thank you. Thank you.

317
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:27,140
Hongling, open the door.

318
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:35,680
Drive!

319
00:19:36,900 --> 00:19:37,780
Excuse me. Excuse me.

320
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:38,620
How are you, ma'am?

321
00:19:43,620 --> 00:19:45,180
He's coming. He's coming.

322
00:19:48,060 --> 00:19:49,300
Sir, where are they?

323
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:50,300
A car drove them away.

324
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:56,500
(Silence  Emergency Room)

325
00:19:57,020 --> 00:19:59,420
Hongling. Don't worry too much.

326
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:00,940
Your mother will be fine.

327
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:07,300
Mom.

328
00:20:08,820 --> 00:20:10,260
Doctor, how is she?

329
00:20:10,540 --> 00:20:11,980
The patient is out of danger.

330
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:13,140
Luckily, it was in time,

331
00:20:13,860 --> 00:20:14,900
but she should be observed
in the hospital.

332
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:16,220
You may go through the formalities.

333
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:17,100
OK.

334
00:20:17,740 --> 00:20:19,220
Thank you, doctor.

335
00:20:19,460 --> 00:20:20,060
Guohua.

336
00:20:20,900 --> 00:20:21,780
I have no money with me.

337
00:20:22,340 --> 00:20:22,820
It's fine.

338
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:23,700
I have some. I'll go for it.

339
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:31,620
Doctor, how is she?

340
00:20:31,900 --> 00:20:32,780
Take her to the ward.

341
00:20:37,300 --> 00:20:38,660
That's all for details.

342
00:20:38,660 --> 00:20:40,100
You won't understand it specifically.

343
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:42,020
That is to say,

344
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:43,980
my mother is in a stable condition,

345
00:20:44,140 --> 00:20:45,700
and can leave the hospital soon,

346
00:20:45,980 --> 00:20:47,820
but the illness is still serious

347
00:20:47,900 --> 00:20:49,620
and can attack and kill her anytime.

348
00:20:49,820 --> 00:20:51,820
Only surgery can cure it.

349
00:20:52,340 --> 00:20:52,780
Yes.

350
00:20:53,620 --> 00:20:55,620
Why doesn't she have the surgery

351
00:20:55,860 --> 00:20:57,470
and leave the hospital
after full recovery?

352
00:20:58,120 --> 00:20:59,130
Cardiac surgery has

353
00:20:59,130 --> 00:21:01,010
high professional requirements
for a doctor.

354
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:01,960
In the country,

355
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:03,560
only Professor Su
who came back from abroad

356
00:21:03,560 --> 00:21:04,520
can do it.

357
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:06,720
We can invite Professor Su then.

358
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,280
As a benevolent doctor,

359
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:09,960
he'd surely help us if we beg him.

360
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:13,240
Professor Su was in poor health
years ago.

361
00:21:13,320 --> 00:21:14,480
He is old now.

362
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:15,240
His energy is limited

363
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:17,080
and he can only do
a few surgeries a year.

364
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:19,360
Patients all over the country
are all waiting in line.

365
00:21:19,600 --> 00:21:21,240
It's hard to get a surgery from him.

366
00:21:25,380 --> 00:21:26,020
Doctor,

367
00:21:26,380 --> 00:21:28,620
without considering other factors,

368
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:30,300
do you suggest my mother

369
00:21:30,380 --> 00:21:31,660
to have the surgery now?

370
00:21:32,260 --> 00:21:34,260
The patient is weak,

371
00:21:34,540 --> 00:21:35,660
but she is still young.

372
00:21:36,060 --> 00:21:37,700
Her other organs and body functions

373
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:38,460
have no problem.

374
00:21:38,820 --> 00:21:40,020
If the conditions are met,

375
00:21:40,020 --> 00:21:41,540
a surgery should be done

376
00:21:41,540 --> 00:21:42,460
to cure her illness and extend her life.

377
00:21:43,020 --> 00:21:45,020
If choosing a conservative treatment,

378
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:45,740
she should be closely observed.

379
00:21:49,420 --> 00:21:50,100
Hongling.

380
00:21:50,860 --> 00:21:51,860
What do you think?

381
00:21:53,580 --> 00:21:54,340
I don't know.

382
00:21:55,740 --> 00:21:57,140
Don't worry too much.

383
00:21:57,580 --> 00:21:59,460
Doctor said there is a way.

384
00:21:59,740 --> 00:22:00,660
Or we can

385
00:22:00,660 --> 00:22:02,700
pull some strings and have the surgery.

386
00:22:03,380 --> 00:22:04,420
Easy for you to say.

387
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:06,260
Patients all over the country
are waiting in line.

388
00:22:07,940 --> 00:22:09,300
Maybe I have an idea.

389
00:22:11,180 --> 00:22:12,380
A comrade-in-arms of my father

390
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:13,660
is the leader of
the military medical university.

391
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:15,820
He knows all the hospitals in Beijing.

392
00:22:16,100 --> 00:22:16,980
He might know

393
00:22:16,980 --> 00:22:18,500
this Professor Su.

394
00:22:18,980 --> 00:22:20,460
I'll tell my father when he gets back.

395
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:27,140
Don't you believe me?

396
00:22:31,220 --> 00:22:31,940
Let's talk later.

397
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:33,660
I can't think clearly now.

398
00:22:36,420 --> 00:22:37,700
But it cannot

399
00:22:38,460 --> 00:22:39,820
be delayed.

400
00:22:40,060 --> 00:22:41,220
The doctor said

401
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:42,780
that cardiac surgery is dangerous.

402
00:22:43,420 --> 00:22:44,820
We should wait

403
00:22:45,380 --> 00:22:47,420
if a proper doctor can't be found.

404
00:22:48,300 --> 00:22:50,300
That's why I wanted
to talk to my father.

405
00:22:51,740 --> 00:22:54,860
The surgery is not urgent.

406
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:57,380
I'm worried

407
00:22:57,380 --> 00:22:59,380
where Hongling should live at night.

408
00:23:00,620 --> 00:23:02,260
Where can she get a room?

409
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:05,700
She might borrow a room smoothly.

410
00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:06,980
The problem is that

411
00:23:07,220 --> 00:23:09,260
she doesn't live just for one day.

412
00:23:09,260 --> 00:23:10,900
I can live in a guesthouse.

413
00:23:11,900 --> 00:23:13,100
Guesthouse?

414
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:14,380
No.

415
00:23:15,260 --> 00:23:16,860
It's not safe for a girl

416
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:17,820
to live in a guesthouse alone.

417
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:18,860
Chunsheng.

418
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:21,100
Do you have an empty room at home?

419
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:25,740
My father isn't at home.

420
00:23:25,860 --> 00:23:27,780
His room has been empty.

421
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:31,860
Chunsheng. It's inconvenient
to be at your home.

422
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:32,500
Besides,

423
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:34,340
Yanqiu is also at home.

424
00:23:34,940 --> 00:23:36,060
Isn't that good?

425
00:23:36,780 --> 00:23:37,900
Girls can

426
00:23:38,180 --> 00:23:39,780
take care of each other.

427
00:23:40,140 --> 00:23:41,300
That sounds good,

428
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:42,020
but...

429
00:23:42,980 --> 00:23:44,900
Hongling, what do you think?

430
00:23:52,300 --> 00:23:53,420
Hongling, come in.

431
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:05,620
(Chunsheng: I went on a business trip.
Be good.  Yanqiu.)

432
00:24:11,700 --> 00:24:12,340
Hongling.

433
00:24:12,860 --> 00:24:14,580
My sister is on a business trip.

434
00:24:15,660 --> 00:24:17,060
You can live in her room.

435
00:24:17,620 --> 00:24:19,100
Use her toiletries

436
00:24:19,100 --> 00:24:20,460
for now.

437
00:24:21,060 --> 00:24:22,420
I'll buy you new ones tomorrow.

438
00:24:25,660 --> 00:24:26,300
Come.

439
00:24:32,300 --> 00:24:34,300
You've had a hard day today.

440
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:36,220
Wash up and go to rest early.

441
00:25:14,940 --> 00:25:15,580
Mom.

442
00:25:16,380 --> 00:25:17,300
Haven't you gone to sleep?

443
00:25:18,900 --> 00:25:19,700
How can I sleep?

444
00:25:20,740 --> 00:25:21,820
What's wrong?

445
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:25,140
What's wrong?

446
00:25:26,060 --> 00:25:27,140
I should ask you.

447
00:25:28,060 --> 00:25:30,460
Did you save someone today?

448
00:25:32,460 --> 00:25:34,300
Wang told you, right?

449
00:25:34,540 --> 00:25:36,260
Don't ask who told me.

450
00:25:36,260 --> 00:25:37,180
I'm asking you.

451
00:25:39,300 --> 00:25:40,060
It's her, right?

452
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:42,940
Mom, her house is on fire.

453
00:25:42,940 --> 00:25:44,460
Her mother had a heart attack.

454
00:25:44,700 --> 00:25:46,420
I ran into them and
sent them to the hospital.

455
00:25:46,460 --> 00:25:47,340
Was that wrong?

456
00:25:48,260 --> 00:25:49,660
I won't argue with you.

457
00:25:50,140 --> 00:25:52,100
Anyway, it's a good thing

458
00:25:52,300 --> 00:25:53,300
that you saved people.

459
00:25:53,300 --> 00:25:53,940
Right?

460
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:56,940
I've discussed it with your father.

461
00:25:57,180 --> 00:25:58,700
Now I officially inform you.

462
00:25:59,100 --> 00:26:00,820
You'll go to Beidaihe next week

463
00:26:00,820 --> 00:26:02,300
for pre-service training.

464
00:26:03,140 --> 00:26:04,860
Hanging around in Beijing all day

465
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:06,180
is no good thing.

466
00:26:08,700 --> 00:26:09,460
Look at yourself.

467
00:26:10,180 --> 00:26:11,580
You should get some lessons.

468
00:26:20,140 --> 00:26:21,340
(A comrade-in-arms of my father)

469
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:22,860
(is the leader of
the military medical university.)

470
00:26:23,020 --> 00:26:24,420
He knows all the hospitals in Beijing.

471
00:26:24,940 --> 00:26:25,820
I'll tell him

472
00:26:25,820 --> 00:26:26,460
after he comes back.

473
00:26:29,060 --> 00:26:29,900
Let's talk later.

474
00:26:30,420 --> 00:26:31,540
(I can't think clearly now.)

475
00:26:59,140 --> 00:27:00,260
Have some vegetables.

476
00:27:03,380 --> 00:27:03,940
Hongling.

477
00:27:04,740 --> 00:27:06,180
I told Guohua this yesterday.

478
00:27:06,940 --> 00:27:08,900
When Heizi sent people to me before,

479
00:27:09,460 --> 00:27:10,980
I told everyone these words.

480
00:27:12,060 --> 00:27:13,340
It's no longer

481
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:15,140
the feudal era.

482
00:27:15,700 --> 00:27:17,780
People are free to love.

483
00:27:18,300 --> 00:27:19,660
Don't listen to anyone,

484
00:27:20,020 --> 00:27:21,980
not to your parents,

485
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:24,380
to Tian, Guohua or me.

486
00:27:24,860 --> 00:27:26,060
Just listen to yourself.

487
00:27:30,500 --> 00:27:31,900
I... I used to

488
00:27:32,900 --> 00:27:34,740
consider many people.

489
00:27:35,340 --> 00:27:36,420
Tian.

490
00:27:37,140 --> 00:27:37,940
Guohua.

491
00:27:39,180 --> 00:27:40,820
Even Heizi and the others.

492
00:27:41,900 --> 00:27:43,020
But recently,

493
00:27:43,380 --> 00:27:44,740
especially what Tian said to me

494
00:27:44,740 --> 00:27:45,820
before he got arrested,

495
00:27:46,340 --> 00:27:47,580
I thought about it carefully.

496
00:27:48,740 --> 00:27:50,140
I don't think that

497
00:27:50,300 --> 00:27:51,140
everything he said is right.

498
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:52,580
He can't

499
00:27:53,060 --> 00:27:55,060
just bring us together as he wants.

500
00:27:55,420 --> 00:27:56,420
The key is...

501
00:27:59,660 --> 00:28:01,180
What is the key?

502
00:28:01,940 --> 00:28:03,380
The key is still on you.

503
00:28:09,940 --> 00:28:11,860
Whether you hesitate now

504
00:28:12,020 --> 00:28:12,940
or have concerns,

505
00:28:13,940 --> 00:28:15,060
I can understand.

506
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:17,540
I don't want to put pressure on you.

507
00:28:18,540 --> 00:28:19,900
Neither does Guohua.

508
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:22,940
You didn't know

509
00:28:23,460 --> 00:28:25,300
ether of us before.

510
00:28:25,940 --> 00:28:27,500
It's not bad to know us more.

511
00:28:28,260 --> 00:28:30,220
I believe Guohua thinks the same.

512
00:28:30,940 --> 00:28:31,860
So,

513
00:28:32,020 --> 00:28:33,140
this thing

514
00:28:33,820 --> 00:28:35,180
is up to you at last.

515
00:28:36,540 --> 00:28:37,660
The two of us

516
00:28:38,340 --> 00:28:38,900
will wait.

517
00:28:42,140 --> 00:28:42,820
Chunsheng.

518
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:44,820
I know you two are both good to me.

519
00:28:45,180 --> 00:28:46,540
I clearly know that.

520
00:28:47,420 --> 00:28:48,820
I'm sorry

521
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:50,580
that I angered you

522
00:28:50,940 --> 00:28:51,820
at the ice rink,

523
00:28:53,700 --> 00:28:55,420
but my heart has never changed.

524
00:28:56,340 --> 00:28:57,020
Chunsheng.

525
00:28:57,940 --> 00:28:58,900
I think you understand.

526
00:29:02,900 --> 00:29:03,580
It's late.

527
00:29:03,900 --> 00:29:05,100
I'm going to visit my mother.

528
00:29:06,860 --> 00:29:07,740
I'm going with you.

529
00:29:09,460 --> 00:29:11,100
(Unit One)

530
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:13,540
Hongling.

531
00:29:14,020 --> 00:29:14,700
Get on.

532
00:29:23,380 --> 00:29:24,100
Let's go.

533
00:29:42,340 --> 00:29:44,060
Guohua, what's the matter?

534
00:29:44,540 --> 00:29:45,780
Dad. Mom.

535
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:47,660
I've decided it.

536
00:29:48,860 --> 00:29:49,660
You're right.

537
00:29:50,340 --> 00:29:51,180
I'm not young.

538
00:29:51,660 --> 00:29:53,140
I can't waste time like this.

539
00:29:53,780 --> 00:29:54,900
I should be

540
00:29:54,900 --> 00:29:56,460
committed to the army,

541
00:29:56,740 --> 00:29:58,180
to learn and get trained.

542
00:29:59,820 --> 00:30:00,860
I want to join the army
as soon as possible.

543
00:30:01,700 --> 00:30:02,780
Good boy.

544
00:30:02,780 --> 00:30:04,780
Look, our son is promising.

545
00:30:04,780 --> 00:30:06,300
I thought I heard him wrong.

546
00:30:06,300 --> 00:30:07,540
It's our son, right?

547
00:30:09,060 --> 00:30:10,100
I can speak for your father.

548
00:30:10,260 --> 00:30:11,700
We agree.

549
00:30:12,220 --> 00:30:14,500
But I have a condition.

550
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:15,340
Say it.

551
00:30:16,180 --> 00:30:18,340
I want to go with Hongling together.

552
00:30:20,180 --> 00:30:21,340
Dad. Mom.

553
00:30:21,740 --> 00:30:22,740
Hear me out first.

554
00:30:23,580 --> 00:30:25,660
Hongling is

555
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:26,940
an excellent violinist.

556
00:30:27,380 --> 00:30:29,300
She's gifted. She loves music.

557
00:30:29,460 --> 00:30:31,220
She's been practicing since young
and has a solid foundation.

558
00:30:32,340 --> 00:30:35,180
Her biggest dream is to join
an art troupe.

559
00:30:35,460 --> 00:30:36,140
I believe

560
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:37,500
she'll become the best player

561
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:40,060
in the art troupe if she can go.

562
00:30:41,060 --> 00:30:43,940
I hope to help her realize her dream.

563
00:30:44,700 --> 00:30:46,460
This is also my biggest wish.

564
00:30:46,700 --> 00:30:47,300
Guohua.

565
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:50,580
You know He Hongling's family.

566
00:30:51,300 --> 00:30:54,500
It would be hard for her
to join the army.

567
00:30:55,100 --> 00:30:55,980
I know, Dad.

568
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:58,460
But her father was wronged.

569
00:30:58,780 --> 00:30:59,460
Besides,

570
00:30:59,820 --> 00:31:01,340
Hongling is outstanding.

571
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:03,860
The army needs such professionals.

572
00:31:04,460 --> 00:31:05,140
It doesn't matter.

573
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:06,940
It can't be in a hurry.

574
00:31:07,780 --> 00:31:09,260
There is still one month left

575
00:31:09,260 --> 00:31:10,180
after the Beidaihe training.

576
00:31:10,900 --> 00:31:11,580
I'll wait.

577
00:31:11,980 --> 00:31:13,780
When this is settled,

578
00:31:14,020 --> 00:31:15,940
then we'll join the army together.

579
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:17,740
Dad. Mom. Do your business.

580
00:31:17,740 --> 00:31:18,500
I'm going to my room.

581
00:31:18,660 --> 00:31:19,820
Wait! You...

582
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:22,140
This kid.

583
00:31:22,260 --> 00:31:23,380
Don't you understand?

584
00:31:23,540 --> 00:31:24,740
This is an ultimatum.

585
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:30,940
(Be vigilant to defend our country)
Is it your idea to go to Beidaihe?

586
00:31:31,340 --> 00:31:31,900
Yes.

587
00:31:32,220 --> 00:31:34,860
Just to separate
your brother and Hongling?

588
00:31:34,860 --> 00:31:36,540
They aren't together.
It's not separation.

589
00:31:36,940 --> 00:31:38,700
I just want them to calm down.

590
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:41,740
Aren't you too nosy about this?

591
00:31:41,740 --> 00:31:42,900
He is my brother.

592
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:44,140
I'm doing it for him.

593
00:31:45,340 --> 00:31:46,540
Don't tell on me.

594
00:31:46,860 --> 00:31:47,900
Or I'll punish you.

595
00:31:48,660 --> 00:31:49,260
Fang.

596
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:51,580
Chen Tao.

597
00:31:52,020 --> 00:31:52,940
I'm looking for you.

598
00:31:55,940 --> 00:31:56,820
This is...

599
00:31:59,020 --> 00:32:01,140
He is my relative, Chen Hongjun.

600
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:03,180
Hello. Hello.

601
00:32:03,500 --> 00:32:04,300
My name is Chen Tao,

602
00:32:04,420 --> 00:32:05,940
Ye Fang's fiance.

603
00:32:11,020 --> 00:32:12,420
Hello, I'm Chen Hongjun.

604
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:13,660
Hello. Hello.

605
00:32:15,220 --> 00:32:17,340
Hongjun, you may go back first.

606
00:32:18,140 --> 00:32:20,540
OK. I'm going then.

607
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:21,900
By the way, Fang.

608
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:23,460
I've been studying Lesson 19.

609
00:32:23,860 --> 00:32:25,020
Lesson 19?

610
00:32:25,820 --> 00:32:26,900
There are two lessons missing.

611
00:32:26,900 --> 00:32:28,500
I intended to bring them to you
in two days.

612
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:29,860
It wouldn't be delayed.

613
00:32:30,420 --> 00:32:31,100
OK.

614
00:32:32,940 --> 00:32:34,820
Are you preparing for
the college entrance exam?

615
00:32:35,100 --> 00:32:35,660
Yes.

616
00:32:36,940 --> 00:32:38,540
There is no such exam.
Do you know it?

617
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:39,700
I know.

618
00:32:40,260 --> 00:32:41,060
But

619
00:32:41,820 --> 00:32:43,060
Ye Fang said there would be one.

620
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:50,900
Do you believe everything she says?

621
00:32:51,900 --> 00:32:52,420
Yes.

622
00:32:55,020 --> 00:32:55,820
That's good.

623
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:59,180
You must be very idle then.

624
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:03,900
Hongjun, aren't you leaving?

625
00:33:05,580 --> 00:33:06,180
Fine.

626
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:07,940
I'm going back then.

627
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:16,580
What are you doing here?

628
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:19,380
I'm here to invite you

629
00:33:19,580 --> 00:33:20,860
