630
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:22,860
No. I have something to do.

631
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:24,740
What is it?

632
00:33:25,380 --> 00:33:26,540
Going to your old house

633
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:28,980
to see this Chen...

634
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:29,820
Chen Hongjun.

635
00:33:30,580 --> 00:33:31,580
Chen Hongjun.

636
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:34,140
What relative is he to you?

637
00:33:34,380 --> 00:33:35,900
You've never mentioned him before.

638
00:33:36,060 --> 00:33:37,540
He is my brother's classmate.

639
00:33:39,180 --> 00:33:39,980
No wonder.

640
00:33:40,060 --> 00:33:40,980
No wonder what?

641
00:33:42,300 --> 00:33:42,900
Ye Fang.

642
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:45,340
I think you should be cautious

