00:33:45,780 --> 00:33:46,540
to make friends.

644
00:33:46,980 --> 00:33:49,020
My brother and he were
primary school classmates.

645
00:33:49,180 --> 00:33:50,580
We've known each other since childhood.

646
00:33:51,060 --> 00:33:52,460
Your brother's classmate?

647
00:33:52,460 --> 00:33:54,060
Wouldn't there be a problem?

648
00:33:54,700 --> 00:33:55,820
What do you mean?

649
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:57,700
I heard that

650
00:33:58,140 --> 00:33:59,700
Guohua was unwilling to join the army

651
00:33:59,940 --> 00:34:01,060
and always hung out

652
00:34:01,460 --> 00:34:04,020
with some bad friends.

653
00:34:04,020 --> 00:34:06,420
He often fought with others.

654
00:34:06,420 --> 00:34:07,060
Chen Tao.

655
00:34:07,460 --> 00:34:09,140
Hongjun and my brother are good people.

656
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:11,100
Don't listen to the nonsense.

657
00:34:11,100 --> 00:34:12,660
Why did he come to Baoding then?

658
00:34:12,860 --> 00:34:13,380
He...

659
00:34:15,660 --> 00:34:17,780
To review lessons in a quiet place.

660
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:20,300
To go to a college?

661
00:34:21,540 --> 00:34:22,460
Is it your idea?

662
00:34:22,700 --> 00:34:23,220
Yeah.

663
00:34:24,180 --> 00:34:24,860
Hey.

664
00:34:25,740 --> 00:34:27,380
Why does he believe everything you say?

665
00:34:27,580 --> 00:34:29,660
You don't believe me, but someone does.

666
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:32,540
He is so good and listens to you.

667
00:34:32,820 --> 00:34:33,900
Why aren't you together with him?

668
00:34:40,060 --> 00:34:41,580
Fang. I didn't mean that.

669
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:42,500
Fang.

670
00:34:44,660 --> 00:34:45,220
Mr. Niu.

671
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:46,180
Chunsheng.

672
00:34:47,380 --> 00:34:48,180
Hello.

673
00:34:48,580 --> 00:34:49,500
Xiao Chunsheng, right?

674
00:34:49,660 --> 00:34:50,460
Yes, I am.

675
00:34:50,460 --> 00:34:51,140
Who are you?

676
00:34:51,140 --> 00:34:53,620
I'm Xu, director of
the Political Department.

677
00:34:53,820 --> 00:34:55,660
The member of your father's task force.

678
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:57,460
My father... He...

679
00:34:57,580 --> 00:34:58,140
What happened to him?

680
00:34:58,140 --> 00:35:00,700
Mr. Xiao Yanpei had
a cerebral infarction last night.

681
00:35:00,700 --> 00:35:02,380
He's been sent to Hospital 301.

682
00:35:02,380 --> 00:35:03,460
Wait. What did you say?

683
00:35:38,740 --> 00:35:39,380
Chunsheng.

684
00:35:40,420 --> 00:35:41,660
The doctor is asking for you.

685
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:04,700
Delivery and rescue were timely.

686
00:36:04,700 --> 00:36:06,140
The patient is out of danger.

687
00:36:06,780 --> 00:36:07,300
Now,

688
00:36:07,300 --> 00:36:09,820
the functions of his body are
recovering well.

689
00:36:09,820 --> 00:36:11,700
He can leave the hospital in a few days.

690
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:13,700
Thank you, doctor.

691
00:36:13,980 --> 00:36:14,980
Chunsheng.

692
00:36:15,700 --> 00:36:17,540
Considering your father's
physical condition,

693
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:19,020
the organization decides

694
00:36:19,300 --> 00:36:21,860
to stop the isolation review of him.

695
00:36:22,140 --> 00:36:22,940
After the treatment,

696
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:24,580
you can take him home

697
00:36:25,220 --> 00:36:25,860
and look after him.

698
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:27,180
Really?

699
00:36:27,900 --> 00:36:28,780
Do you mean

700
00:36:29,100 --> 00:36:30,740
my father's thing is settled?

701
00:36:32,660 --> 00:36:33,580
Not yet.

702
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:35,740
But I believe

703
00:36:36,140 --> 00:36:37,900
the organization will conclude it soon.

704
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:38,940
Rest assured.

705
00:36:39,180 --> 00:36:40,940
Wait patiently for a while.

706
00:36:44,060 --> 00:36:44,820
Thanks.

707
00:36:47,020 --> 00:36:48,900
Thanks for the organization's care.

708
00:36:50,180 --> 00:36:50,780
Thanks.

709
00:36:51,660 --> 00:36:52,540
Did your father

710
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:54,820
