711
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:57,860
Yes, sometimes he thought he was

712
00:36:58,220 --> 00:36:59,860
still in the time of the liberation war.

713
00:37:01,300 --> 00:37:02,460
He is old,

714
00:37:02,580 --> 00:37:04,260
and had a stroke.

715
00:37:04,820 --> 00:37:06,260
After he leaves the hospital,

716
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:07,420
the intermittent amnesia

717
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:09,900
and cognitive disorder may intensify.

718
00:37:09,900 --> 00:37:12,340
He might forget you completely.

719
00:37:14,140 --> 00:37:15,740
Be mentally prepared for that.

720
00:37:20,220 --> 00:37:20,780
Don't worry.

721
00:37:21,060 --> 00:37:22,420
We can surely take good care of him.

722
00:37:31,460 --> 00:37:32,300
Who?

723
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:34,260
Thanks.

724
00:37:34,460 --> 00:37:35,220
You're welcome.

725
00:37:52,740 --> 00:37:53,380
Hongling.

726
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:54,780
Guohua.

727
00:37:55,780 --> 00:37:56,460
Here you are.

728
00:37:56,660 --> 00:37:57,540
How is he?

729
00:37:57,700 --> 00:37:59,020
He's been out of danger.

730
00:37:59,700 --> 00:38:00,340
That's good.

731
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:08,860
Have you visited your mother?

732
00:38:09,220 --> 00:38:09,940
Yes. Just now.

733
00:38:10,220 --> 00:38:12,060
The nurse you arranged
for my mother is good.

734
00:38:12,220 --> 00:38:13,180
Thank you very much.

735
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:15,580
No thanks between us.

736
00:38:16,420 --> 00:38:17,060
Well.

737
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:18,820
I contacted a nursing home
for your mother.

738
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:21,020
She can recuperate there.

739
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:23,140
I'm also contacting Professor Su.

740
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:24,340
Once I contact him,

741
00:38:24,340 --> 00:38:26,180
your mother can have the surgery.

742
00:38:27,300 --> 00:38:27,940
Guohua.

743
00:38:28,340 --> 00:38:29,780
Thanks for what you did

744
00:38:29,940 --> 00:38:30,620
for my mother.

745
00:38:31,260 --> 00:38:32,100
Again.

746
00:38:32,180 --> 00:38:33,780
I said no thanks.

747
00:38:34,740 --> 00:38:36,020
Oh, Hongling.

748
00:38:36,460 --> 00:38:38,100
I'm going to Beidaihe

749
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:39,620
for the pre-service training.

750
00:38:39,820 --> 00:38:40,580
Before I go,

751
00:38:41,020 --> 00:38:42,340
I want to ask you something.

752
00:38:42,700 --> 00:38:43,580
What is it?

753
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:46,380
Do you want to join the army

754
00:38:46,580 --> 00:38:47,820
and go to the art troupe?

755
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:53,740
I'm going. They're urging me.

756
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:55,060
Think about it.

757
00:39:24,260 --> 00:39:26,300
Xiaomei. How to use this?

758
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:28,700
Let me do it.

759
00:39:38,860 --> 00:39:39,820
Can it be sold?

760
00:39:40,420 --> 00:39:41,940
No. Blood pressure monitors
are in short supply.

761
00:39:42,180 --> 00:39:43,820
