00:42:03,860 --> 00:42:05,340
What should I say?

827
00:42:05,820 --> 00:42:06,660
Say nothing.

828
00:42:07,300 --> 00:42:08,060
I'm leaving then.

829
00:42:08,340 --> 00:42:09,340
- OK. Thanks.
- Thanks.

